      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-qta-frz-000      thru acc-qta-frz-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-key    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-key-reg-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-key-reg-300.
       acc-key-reg-800.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
